The system allows the creation of a quote or purchase order from the spare parts used in the work request.
The functions are available through the "Purchase Lines" item in work requests.


### Copy From Work Request

Copy spare parts from the work request.

### Create Purchase Document

Allows to create a quote or purchase order with the vendor specified in the lines.

### Open Purchase Document

Allows to view or edit the generated purchase document.

### Create Requistition Request

Allows to create a requisition request with the specified lines.

### Open Requistition Request

Allows to view or edit the generated requisition request.